{"tid":668383,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★估公司！沽空大鱷另起爐灶　「頭炮」選港上市公司","createTime":"2018-05-17T14:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T15:27:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"4e73fd20a664c11d823eaff26f528aefe2ab4024","tid":668383,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"沽空機構格勞克斯（Glaucus Research）前研究部總監Soren Aandahl另起爐灶，成立以太平洋殺人鯨命名的維權基金Blue Orca Capital，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">揚言會狙擊一家香港上市公司</span></span>，作為新基金的「頭炮」。香港證監會發言人回覆《東網》查詢時表示不就個別事件作出評論。<br />\n<br />\nSoren Aandahl先後狙擊過的港股包括西部水泥(02233)、旭光新材料(00067)、浩澤淨水(02014)、瑞年控股(02010)、德普科技(03823)及中滔環保(01363)等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180517/bkn-20180517212129386-0517_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180517%2Fbkn-20180517212129386-0517_00842_001.html&d=CjZ%2F%2FeBCvDBHkUoqNCXKLp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=64250632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180517/bkn-20180517212129386-0517_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"953824b241a18a5389eaac138888a87bf5653157","tid":668383,"uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:40:38.000Z","msg":"700?"},{"pid":"7eedc837e6741c691c939738ffa4c0f4e7268dbf","tid":668383,"uid":109386,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"佢有西咁多錢j激700咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbb2140168a6177017be9a9662b83e00536d708","tid":668383,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"953824b241a18a5389eaac138888a87bf5653157","tid":668383,"uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:40:38.000Z","msg":"700?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"今日2千幾萬 424位 買700<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" clas